<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Logged Out</title>
<style>body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;background:#f5f5f5;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;margin:0;}.card{background:white;border-radius:8px;padding:40px;max-width:400px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.1);}</style>
</head><body><div class="card"><h2>Logged Out</h2><p>You have been logged out. Your access to restricted content has been revoked.</p><p style="color:#6c757d;font-size:14px;">This window will close automatically.</p></div>
<script>setTimeout(function() { window.close(); }, 2000);</script>
</body></html>
